org.sql: SELECT statuses.id, statuses.updated_at FROM statuses INNER JOIN status_pins ON statuses.id = status_pins.status_id WHERE statuses.deleted_at IS NULL AND status_pins.account_id = "$1" AND statuses.visibility IN ("$2", "$3") ORDER BY status_pins.created_at DESC

rewrites.sql: SELECT statuses.id, statuses.updated_at FROM statuses INNER JOIN status_pins ON statuses.id = status_pins.status_id WHERE statuses.deleted_at IS NULL AND status_pins.account_id = "$1" AND statuses.visibility IN ("$2", "$3") ORDER BY status_pins.created_at DESC LIMIT 1
